The first attempt to translate Bible into [[Kannada]] was by the Serampore missionaries and they appear to have it completed by 1809. However this manuscript was lost in the 1812 [[Serampore Mission Press#Fire at the press|fire at the Serampore press]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bsind.org/kannada.html|title=Kannada Bible|publisher=Bible Society of India|accessdate=8 January 2015}}</ref>
Some parts of the Bible were translated into [[Kannada]] in 1812. In 1823 The New Testament was published. In 1831 the complete Bible was published in Kannada.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldscriptures.org/pages/kannada.html|title=The Bible in Kannada|publisher=Worldscriptures.org|accessdate=7 December 2014}}</ref> Translators included [[John Hands]], founder of the [[London Missionary Society]] station in [[Bellary]] in 1810, and [[William Reeve (missionary)|William Reeve]] at Bellary and [[Bangalore]].<ref>''Literary autobiography of C. P. Brown'' Charles Philip Brown, ed. Golla Narayanaswami Reddy, Bangorey - 1978 "REEVE, William (1794-1850): LMS missionary at Bellary and Bangalore: well-versed in Canarese: his Carnataca & English Dictionary appeared in 1832 (revised by D. Sanderson in 1858): along with Hands translated Bible into Canarese."</ref>
A revised version of the New Testament was published in 1850, and a further revised version was released in 1854. The [[London Missionary Society|LMS]] missionaries continued the work and the complete Bible was published by the year 1865. The revision of this Bible was handled by a committee and was released by 1934. This is the version still being used [http://bsind.org/kannada.html].
In collaboration with ''Church centric bible translation'', Free Bibles India has published an [http://freebiblesindia.com/bible/kn/ Kannada translation online].
In 2009, the New Testament of [[New World Translation of the Holy Scriptures]] was released by [[Jehovah's Witnesses]] in Kannada.<ref>"WatchTower publications", Watchtower publications Index (1986-2009)</ref> It was [https://wol.jw.org/kn/wol/binav/r167/lp-ka/bi7/KA/2009 published online] (also offline in [https://download-a.akamaihd.net/files/media_bible/fd/bi7_KA.pdf PDF format]) with mobile versions released through ''JW Library'' application in App stores.
==Example== {{quotation|John 3:16 ದೇವರು ಲೋಕವನ್ನು ಎಷ್ಟೋ ಪ್ರೀತಿಮಾಡಿ ತನ್ನ ಒಬ್ಬನೇ ಮಗನನ್ನು ಕೊಟ್ಟನು; ಆತನನ್ನು ನಂಬುವ ಯಾವನಾದರೂ ನಾಶವಾಗದೆ ನಿತ್ಯಜೀವ ವನ್ನು ಪಡೆದವನಾಗಿರುವನು. Dēvaru lōkavannu eṣṭō prītimāḍi tanna obbanē maganannu koṭṭanu; ātanannu nambuva yāvanādarū nāśavāgade nityajīva vannu paḍedavanāgiruvanu.}}
