'''Muangphe''' ([[Exonym and endonym|autonym]]: ''{{IPA|muaŋ˥˧}}'', ''{{IPA|muaŋ˥phe˨˩}}'') is a [[Lolo-Burmese languages|Lolo-Burmese language]] spoken by about 300 people in [[Guangnan County]], [[Yunnan]], China.
