| {{IPA|*-∅}} || {{IPA|*-ʔ}}  || {{IPA|*-s}}   || {{IPA|*-ks}}    || {{IPA|*-k}}  || {{IPA|*-ŋ}} || {{IPA|*-ŋʔ}} || {{IPA|*-ŋs}}
