==Numerals==
Äynu numerals are borrowed from [[Persian language|Persian]]{{citation needed|date=October 2018}}:

* 1 - yäk
* 2 - du
* 3 - si
* 4 - čar
* 5 - pänǰ
* 6 - šäš
* 7 - häp(t)
* 8 - häš(t)
* 9 - noh
* 10 - dah
* 20 - bist
* 100 - säd
* 1000 - hazar

